---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<!-- Disclaimer strip -->
<div style="background: rgb(var(--ink)); color: rgb(var(--paper));">
  <div class="container-x py-4 flex items-start gap-3">
    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" style="color: rgb(var(--clay)); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 3px;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
    <p class="text-[12.5px] leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(var(--paper) / 0.78);">
      I contenuti di questo sito sono esclusivamente informativi e non costituiscono consulenza legale, fiscale o contabile.
      Il filing e il servizio di registered agent in Florida sono erogati da un partner statunitense indipendente.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer style="background: rgb(var(--paper-deep));">

  <!-- Mega claim editoriale -->
  <div class="container-x pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-end">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8">
        <span class="chapter">— Vuoi parlarne</span>
        <h2 class="display mt-6 max-w-[14ch]">
          Scrivici. È il <em>passo più semplice</em>.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 md:text-right">
        <a href="/contatti/" class="btn btn-primary btn-arrow px-6 py-3.5">
          Richiedi informazioni
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <div class="mt-5">
          <a href="mailto:[EMAIL]" class="link-line text-ink text-[15px]">[EMAIL]</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rule"></div>

  <!-- Columns -->
  <div class="container-x py-16 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
    <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="logomark">F</span>
        <span class="font-serif text-[17px]">[NOME BRAND]</span>
      </a>
      <p class="mt-6 text-[14.5px] leading-relaxed max-w-sm text-ink-soft">
        Portale italiano per il company setup amministrativo in Florida.
        Coordiniamo il filing con un partner USA indipendente.
        <strong class="text-ink">Non siamo uno studio legale.</strong>
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="LinkedIn"
          class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-colors hover:bg-ash"
          style="box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgb(var(--hairline-hard));">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 0h-14C2.2 0 0 2.2 0 5v14c0 2.8 2.2 5 5 5h14c2.8 0 5-2.2 5-5V5c0-2.8-2.2-5-5-5zM8 19H5V8h3v11zM6.5 6.7c-.97 0-1.75-.78-1.75-1.75S5.53 3.2 6.5 3.2s1.75.78 1.75 1.75S7.47 6.7 6.5 6.7zM20 19h-3v-5.6c0-3.4-4-3.1-4 0V19h-3V8h3v1.8c1.4-2.6 7-2.8 7 2.5V19z"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-2">
      <h4 class="eyebrow">Servizio</h4>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2.5 text-[14px]">
        <li><a href="/company-setup-florida/" class="link-underline text-ink">Company Setup</a></li>
        <li><a href="/company-setup-florida/llc/" class="link-underline text-ink">LLC in Florida</a></li>
        <li><a href="/company-setup-florida/corporation/" class="link-underline text-ink">Corporation</a></li>
        <li><a href="/company-setup-florida/pacchetti/" class="link-underline text-ink">Pacchetti</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-2">
      <h4 class="eyebrow">Risorse</h4>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2.5 text-[14px]">
        <li><a href="/come-funziona/" class="link-underline text-ink">Il processo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/registered-agent/" class="link-underline text-ink">Partner Florida</a></li>
        <li><a href="/business-in-florida/" class="link-underline text-ink">Editoriale</a></li>
        <li><a href="/manifesto/" class="link-underline text-ink">Manifesto</a></li>
        <li><a href="/faq/" class="link-underline text-ink">FAQ</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-2">
      <h4 class="eyebrow">Contatti</h4>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2.5 text-[14px]">
        <li><a href="/contatti/" class="link-underline text-ink">Scrivici</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:[EMAIL]" class="link-underline text-ink-soft">[EMAIL]</a></li>
        <li class="text-ink-soft">[TELEFONO]</li>
        <li class="text-ink-soft">[INDIRIZZO IT]</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-2">
      <h4 class="eyebrow">Legale</h4>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2.5 text-[14px]">
        <li><a href="/disclaimer/" class="link-underline text-ink">Disclaimer</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy-policy/" class="link-underline text-ink">Privacy</a></li>
        <li><a href="/terms-of-use/" class="link-underline text-ink">Terms</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cookie-policy/" class="link-underline text-ink">Cookie</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rule"></div>

  <!-- Bottom strip -->
  <div class="container-x py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-3 text-[12.5px] text-ink-mute">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <span>© {year} [NOME BRAND]</span>
      <span class="opacity-40">·</span>
      <span>Tutti i diritti riservati</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <span style="display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgb(var(--clay));"></span>
      <span>Made for italians, filed in Florida.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Watermark gigante (decorativo, raffinato) -->
  <div class="container-x pb-2 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="select-none pointer-events-none" style="font-family: 'Fraunces Variable', serif; font-size: clamp(5rem, 18vw, 16rem); line-height: 0.85; letter-spacing: -0.05em; color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgb(var(--hairline-hard)); font-variation-settings: 'SOFT' 30, 'opsz' 144; font-style: italic;">
      Florida<span style="color: rgb(var(--clay) / 0.4); -webkit-text-stroke: 0;">.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
